# Commands

Install LXD
>>   sudo apt install lxd -y

# Intialize LXD
>> lxd init

>> lxc --help
>> lxd --version
>> lxc list

# Launch Ubuntu Container

>> lxc launch ubuntu: 
>> lxc list

>> lxc exec <container> bash 
>> lsb_release -a
>> cat /etc/issue

# Launch Specific ubuntu Version

>> lxc  launch ubuntu:21.04 hirsute
>> lxc exec hirsute -- cat /etc/issue
>> lxc exec hirsute -- lsb_release -a

## Available Linux Container Images

See here --> https://us.lxd.images.canonical.com

# Create Alpine Container

>> lxc launch images:alpine/3.10/amd64 alpine
>> lxc list
>> lxc exec alpine -- cat /etc/issue
>> lxc exec alpine -- lsb_release -a

Exercise create a centos 8 container
